  <h1>Introduction to FrameAPI</h1>
  
  <p class="lead text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-8">
    FrameAPI is a modern backend framework designed to help developers build scalable, maintainable, and secure web applications with ease.
  </p>
  
  <h2>What is FrameAPI?</h2>
  
  <p>
    FrameAPI is a robust Node.js framework for building backend applications and APIs. It provides a clean, expressive API that abstracts away many of the common challenges in backend development, allowing you to focus on building your application's core features.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    The framework is designed with developer experience as a top priority, while also ensuring your applications are performant, secure, and maintainable in the long run.
  </p>
  
  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Elegant Routing</strong> - Simple, expressive routing system that supports parameters, nested routes, and middleware.</li>
    <li><strong>Powerful Middleware</strong> - Flexible middleware system for handling cross-cutting concerns.</li>
    <li><strong>MVC Architecture</strong> - Support for Model-View-Controller pattern to organize your application logic.</li>
    <li><strong>Database Agnostic</strong> - Work with SQL, NoSQL, and graph databases through a unified API.</li>
    <li><strong>Built-in Security</strong> - Comprehensive security features to protect your applications from common vulnerabilities.</li>
    <li><strong>Real-time Support</strong> - First-class support for WebSockets and Server-Sent Events.</li>
    <li><strong>Testing Utilities</strong> - Built-in testing tools to ensure your application works correctly.</li>
    <li><strong>Extensive Documentation</strong> - Comprehensive documentation and examples to get you started quickly.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>Why Choose FrameAPI?</h2>
  
  <p>
    There are many backend frameworks available today, so why choose FrameAPI? Here are a few reasons:
  </p>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Developer Experience</strong> - Designed to make developers productive and happy.</li>
    <li><strong>Performance</strong> - Built with performance in mind at every level of the stack.</li>
    <li><strong>Security</strong> - Security best practices are baked into the framework.</li>
    <li><strong>Scalability</strong> - From small prototypes to enterprise applications, FrameAPI scales with your needs.</li>
    <li><strong>Community</strong> - Active community of developers and maintainers.</li>
  </ul>
  
